entries.text: Your web support advisor today is Thorley, from the XYZ Live Chat team

Address has been confirmed as #NUM Wavell Way, Huntington, Chester, Cheshire, #ALNUM #ALNUM

To make this change from today until renewal results in an additional premium of #NUM This is due to the change in address and moving one of the vehicles to be kept on the street overnight. This means your monthly payments will change from #NUM to #NUM with the next effected payment being on #ALNUM
That's fine please go ahead
Ok, will do that now for you.
Your amended policy documents will appear in your online account in the next #NUM minutes or so.
That's all been done for you.
Is there anything else I can help you with today
That was all, thank you.
Great, enjoy your new home. If theres anything else, please come back to us via chat.
Thank you for chatting with me today. #ALNUM love to know what you think of our chat service. If #ALNUM happy to answer a few quick questions, click on #ALNUM #ALNUM
